{"tid":1914964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtube：家下你唔遵守我訂立既規矩，黃標你咪黃標你，洗同你客氣？","createTime":"2020-03-08T00:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T05:41:41.000Z","uid":9031,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"53db8b483d0e81792dda79ed4e54f5e46cfa1b2b","tid":1914964,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"唔岩咪拉大隊走囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點駁好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYouTube刪影片挨告 「有權審查」勝訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6KvWk1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6KvWk1.png&h=605f104e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【國際中心╱綜合外電報導】美國法院前天對一個有關網路平台言論審查的關鍵案例做出裁定，支持谷歌（Google）等科技巨擘有權依其所願審查其私人平台上的內容，並不牴觸美國《憲法》第一修正案。<br />\n<br />\n儘管使用者達20億 仍屬私人論壇<br />\n<br />\n美國保守派非營利組織PragerU常在Google旗下的影片分享平台YouTube發表短片，推廣爭議性的保守派觀點，先前告上法院，抱怨YouTube非法限制用戶接觸其討論墮胎、槍枝持有權、伊斯蘭教及恐怖主義等主題的影片，但未限制自由派帳號發表類似影片，控YouTube違憲。<br />\n位於加州舊金山的第九巡迴上訴法院前天將該案駁回。法院指出，美國《憲法》第一修正案禁止政府限制人民言論自由，儘管YouTube每月使用者達20億，仍屬於私人論壇，並非受第一修正案規範、受司法監督的公眾論壇。<br />\nYouTube對判決表示支持。PragerU則指控法院「懼怕巨人Google的力量」。美國保守派人士常抱怨谷歌和臉書有反保守派傾向，連美國總統川普也批評Google對他有偏見。司法部前訴訟長韋瑞利指出，法院判決持續表明Google、YouTube及臉書等私人企業不受第一修正案規範，若觀點被逆轉，恐造成網路充滿色情、暴力影像、仇恨言論及旨在貶低傷害他人的詞彙。"},{"pid":"5ad3409905b6d517fe17846aea12321e49ebb6d0","tid":1914964,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:32:08.000Z","msg":"借位 大家幫手推一推<br />\n［行動post入黎推一推］ 明天1930將軍澳*準時到*<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1914250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1914250</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9f5c6588dad64478fbccabb963065be1fbee420","tid":1914964,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"私人公司，駁5刀<br />\n吾通你屌7大公報奶共咩<br />\n最多杯葛佢"},{"pid":"b2c2ae0bd23a37bec0152f7a41cfdbc77ed4b9c3","tid":1914964,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:39:38.000Z","msg":"有權唔做你生意"},{"pid":"5745fb95ae979f5cb60574d6f012737336eabb2e","tid":1914964,"uid":25973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"公眾論壇同私人論壇既定義<br />\n<br />\nutube係唔洗登入都睇到 某程度上都幾公眾下<br />\n<br />\n私人到全球都用緊 真係有幾私人阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都避到1st amendment <br />\n<br />\n算啦搬去支那做國企咪好囉 官司都唔洗打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d25058ffea762d6ddb100e4623152a4c93ef1b9","tid":1914964,"uid":108269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"問題你冇咁平台取代到佢，佢惡晒"},{"pid":"b91db38fa867811571b84bb69a908789955cac16","tid":1914964,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"美國公司都奶共<br />\n基本上你無得應對<br />\n唯有希望下世投胎個世界唔再奶共"},{"pid":"ccd0c9e88a7081656cc7b76cf5ece533a8c76783","tid":1914964,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"咁惡咪打「壟斷」要佢分拆囉！"},{"pid":"87df8573af94840255d819304adab713ed579a78","tid":1914964,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:56:50.000Z","msg":"可以轉去twitch<br />\n<br />\ntwitch就係咁既<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/videos/563490487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fvideos%2F563490487&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=a83971d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/videos/563490487</a>"},{"pid":"3fd70ef16df8c65331629fa1e60c9a4a55e8bac4","tid":1914964,"uid":64073,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"